i had just walked outside my girlfriends home near the forest 
of nisene marks state park about 3 miles from the epicenter 
there was no reason we talked about it later we had just walked 
outside 
i immediately said i hope the center was underneath my feet 
otherwise there are going to be a lot of people dead 
i immediately began to shake i dont believe ive stopped yet 
it seems to me that the ground shakes every once in a while but no 
one else feels it 
it seemed to me the ground went down 2 feet then immediately it 
came back up and kind of rolled around it was like the ocean going 
through the ground you could hear it coming then you feel it 
then you hear it go up there 
the worst part of the whole thing was not the earthquake it 
was over suddenly and it was done the aftershocks were a terror 
