also to be replaced is the section of lower roadway that took 
the brunt of the impact when the upper level fell open 
the lifting and lowering of the damaged section took only 20 
minutes and cables prevented the section from swaying in light 
winds 
the entire upper section measures 74 feet long and 50 feet wide 
